title: Doctor Who Complete Season 03, 1965-1966, William Hartnell
description:
All 45 episodes of the 1965/66 season of Doctor Who, featuring the First Doctor and his companions: Vicki, Steven Taylor, Katarina, Sara Kingdom, Dorothea "Dodo" Chaplet, Polly, and Ben Jackson.

Includes reconstructions using photographs taken on set and recovered segments of footage, along with the audio recordings of the episodes, to recreate missing episodes. Visual quality varies depending on the reconstruction.
